WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.827
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 17=

01:30.827 --> 01:35.273
(- You're the best.
- I'm the best.)

01:40.008 --> 01:42.348
There are people fishing over there.
Let's take a look.

01:42.348 --> 01:43.387
Okay.

01:48.887 --> 01:49.887
Let's go.

02:06.927 --> 02:08.267
Hello, Sir.

02:09.207 --> 02:12.387
May I ask if your fishing rods
are available for rent?

02:12.927 --> 02:14.748
You're Yuerong Manor's guests, right?

02:16.528 --> 02:21.028
Feel free to catch some fish.
No need for any rent, come on.

02:22.368 --> 02:23.047
Be careful.

02:23.047 --> 02:23.848
Thank you.

02:23.848 --> 02:26.268
I made it by myself.
It's not so professional.

02:26.268 --> 02:30.628
We're not any fishing experts.
We don't need something sophisticated.

02:31.167 --> 02:32.788
Okay, we won't bother you.
We'll be over there.

02:32.788 --> 02:33.648
Okay.

02:33.648 --> 02:34.207
Thank you.

02:34.207 --> 02:35.827
Thanks. Let's go.

02:39.968 --> 02:41.547
- How about here?
- Okay.

02:43.128 --> 02:45.327
Be careful. Right here.

02:45.327 --> 02:46.348
Okay.

02:49.447 --> 02:50.808
I don't know how to do it.

02:50.808 --> 02:53.628
It wouldn't be fun if you knew how.

03:00.327 --> 03:01.387
Thank you.

03:01.968 --> 03:05.188
You haven't thrown the hook yet.
Why are you sitting down?

03:07.368 --> 03:08.728
I said I don't know how.

03:08.728 --> 03:09.908
I'll help you.

03:18.368 --> 03:20.508
Alright, throw it now.

03:31.688 --> 03:32.748
Do it again.

03:41.408 --> 03:42.408
Come on.

03:49.848 --> 03:51.147
Is it okay like this?

04:05.928 --> 04:08.188
Do you think I can catch a fish?

04:09.128 --> 04:10.188
It depends.

04:12.767 --> 04:17.012
I'm a traveler from afar. I've never
crossed paths with the fish here.

04:17.012 --> 04:20.428
I doubt if I can catch any.

04:20.967 --> 04:22.267
Hard to say.

04:57.407 --> 04:59.587
Watch the float, not me.

05:05.355 --> 05:10.450
♪ There should be a great fire in fate ♪

05:10.450 --> 05:15.069
♪ To outshine the beautiful landscape ♪

05:16.207 --> 05:18.587
Why choose such a sad song?

05:19.168 --> 05:20.787
It calms my mind.

05:25.438 --> 05:29.904
♪ If our encounter means comedown ♪

05:29.904 --> 05:34.428
♪ Hope we can exchange sickness
for dreams ♪

05:34.488 --> 05:38.548
But if you can't catch fish,
isn't that more upsetting?

05:44.830 --> 05:50.007
♪ The flower will remember it ♪

05:50.007 --> 05:53.564
♪ It falls on my shoulder
as I rest by your side ♪

05:53.808 --> 05:54.907
Are you hot?

05:56.568 --> 05:57.628
I'm okay.

06:28.048 --> 06:29.387
Son.

06:31.407 --> 06:32.988
Caught any fish?

06:37.087 --> 06:38.347
Not yet.

06:49.527 --> 06:51.128
- Hello?
- Mr. Mo.

06:51.128 --> 06:52.807
It's really urgent.

06:52.807 --> 06:53.828
What?

06:53.828 --> 06:57.587
Let Sheng do the vocal harmony.
We really can't find anyone else.

06:58.647 --> 07:01.328
Okay, I get it. Let me ask her.

07:03.608 --> 07:04.707
Bye.

07:09.847 --> 07:11.108
Is something wrong?

07:11.108 --> 07:14.628
Feishao discussed
a new plan for the theme song.

07:16.327 --> 07:18.288
They want you to help them
with the harmony.

07:18.288 --> 07:19.988
Me?

07:21.008 --> 07:21.907
I can't.

07:21.907 --> 07:23.988
You haven't tried.

07:25.248 --> 07:31.587
I haven't performed live once.
Let alone a show this big.

07:32.207 --> 07:33.328
There is always a first time.

07:33.328 --> 07:36.248
But it can't be your 10th Anniversary.

07:36.248 --> 07:39.807
What's wrong with it?

07:39.807 --> 07:45.032
Your dubbing team is famous.
Every actor has millions of fans.

07:45.032 --> 07:51.387
This Anniversary must be perfect.
We can't afford to make mistakes. And...

07:53.048 --> 07:54.267
And what?

07:55.168 --> 07:59.827
I'm worried our relationship will
become the topic of their discussion.

08:01.647 --> 08:06.428
So? We truly are in a relationship.

08:07.808 --> 08:11.188
We can't stop people from
saying whatever they want.

08:13.488 --> 08:20.628
To put it nicely, you're being neutral.
But the fact is, you're indifferent.

08:22.448 --> 08:29.707
Wang Ke wanted you. He heard our choir,
and he knows you are new to this.

08:29.707 --> 08:35.508
So he asked me. Just the harmony.
They'll support you.

08:39.647 --> 08:42.627
And they invited you here this time.

08:42.627 --> 08:46.747
This is Guilin, and they can't
call someone over from afar right now.

08:46.747 --> 08:48.772
They tried to find someone
around here as much as they can.

08:48.772 --> 08:51.142
But the demos are not satisfactory.

08:51.300 --> 08:53.910
You're the best choice.

08:55.767 --> 08:57.228
I also think you can do it.

08:58.248 --> 09:02.348
My first time was also an accident
while helping a friend.

09:04.047 --> 09:05.468
You are helping them, too.

09:06.328 --> 09:11.187
Give it a try.
After all, it's a memory, right?

09:15.208 --> 09:16.787
You are very persuasive.

09:19.407 --> 09:22.228
I admit that.

09:27.167 --> 09:28.468
Son.

09:29.128 --> 09:31.387
I have some oil tea here.
Let's drink it together.

09:32.088 --> 09:33.388
No, thank you.

09:33.388 --> 09:39.508
Come on, you're Yangshuo's guests.
I'll treat you to a cup of tea.

09:39.508 --> 09:41.187
Okay, thank you.

09:42.527 --> 09:44.288
So, what should we do with this rod?

09:44.288 --> 09:45.547
Here, give it to me.

09:50.167 --> 09:51.167
Okay.

09:54.287 --> 09:55.287
Thank you.

09:55.887 --> 10:00.227
I have had butter tea. Their names
sound similar, but they look different.

10:00.227 --> 10:01.747
- Here in Guilin,
- Thank you.

10:01.747 --> 10:09.188
it's available everywhere. It's fried
with ginger and garlic, then boiled.

10:09.188 --> 10:10.528
It's spicy?

10:10.528 --> 10:12.907
Don't drink it yet. There's more.

10:14.407 --> 10:15.028
Here.

10:15.028 --> 10:16.048
Thank you.

10:16.048 --> 10:18.607
It's popcorn and crispy nuts.
You can eat it.

10:18.607 --> 10:19.288
Thank you.

10:19.288 --> 10:20.468
Drink it now.

10:22.488 --> 10:28.987
You may not be used to this at first.
It's humid and rainy here,

10:28.987 --> 10:31.067
but the oil tea can clear damp.

10:33.848 --> 10:35.668
You have a bite!

10:35.668 --> 10:37.267
Quick, take it.

10:49.488 --> 10:50.988
It's a big fish!

11:01.488 --> 11:03.508
Such a big fish!

11:04.567 --> 11:07.868
What a big fish! So, you can fish.

11:07.868 --> 11:11.208
When I was a kid, I lacked patience,
so my dad had me fish.

11:11.208 --> 11:12.508
Let me take a look.

11:13.968 --> 11:15.988
Here's a gift.

11:16.527 --> 11:20.168
Take this back to Yuerong Manor
and let the chef cook it for you.

11:20.168 --> 11:23.307
I just wanted my girlfriend
to experience the joy of fishing.

11:24.167 --> 11:25.628
Not just for the fish.

11:26.887 --> 11:29.167
Can I really take it?
This is what you guys caught.

11:29.167 --> 11:31.388
But the fishing rod and bait
are all yours.

11:31.388 --> 11:33.907
Well, thank you.

11:35.008 --> 11:40.907
Take this. I made it myself.
It definitely has a better taste.

11:42.407 --> 11:43.527
You guys take it.

11:43.527 --> 11:44.028
Thank you.

11:44.028 --> 11:45.108
Thank you.

11:47.767 --> 11:49.508
Here, come and taste it.

11:49.508 --> 11:51.147
What is this?

11:51.728 --> 11:52.648
Oil tea.

11:52.648 --> 11:53.847
Oil tea?

11:53.847 --> 11:54.908
Where did it come from?

11:54.908 --> 11:55.948
It was a gift.

11:55.948 --> 11:56.888
Gift?

11:56.888 --> 11:58.348
From whom?

12:00.287 --> 12:01.508
It's a long story.

12:01.508 --> 12:02.547
Sit.

12:04.968 --> 12:07.868
Just in time, you're back.
Here's the thing.

12:09.047 --> 12:12.456
We need a 24-hour live broadcast
of behind-the-scenes before performance.

12:12.456 --> 12:17.348
This is the cameraman, Mr. Luan.
Now we need a host.

12:17.348 --> 12:20.268
I can't do it. Can anyone cover for me?

12:20.268 --> 12:23.408
We're saving our voices for later.
We can't keep talking before the show.

12:23.408 --> 12:25.548
Neither can us. We have to warm up.

12:25.548 --> 12:28.348
Yeah, Sheng can't do it, too.

12:31.792 --> 12:33.344
(Ten years of dreams and love)

12:33.368 --> 12:38.708
How is hosting so hard?
Who can do it then? I can't do it.

12:47.248 --> 12:50.848
Then it must be me and Mu.
Because we're the most handsome.

12:50.848 --> 12:51.407
You are.

12:51.407 --> 12:52.708
Did I say yes?

12:52.708 --> 12:56.198
We're partners. Without you,
they will think we came into conflict.

12:56.198 --> 12:57.648
It's too troublesome to explain.

12:57.648 --> 13:02.628
Besides, it's a 24-hour live stream.
I can't do it all by myself.

13:02.628 --> 13:06.587
Okay, then I'll play Shen Ce this time.
You play the villain.

13:06.587 --> 13:08.928
Didn't we agree
that you would play the villain?

13:08.928 --> 13:10.167
Can I drink this directly?

13:10.167 --> 13:16.248
Pour this in too. It's edible.
He said the tea can clear damp.

13:16.248 --> 13:18.628
Any disposable cups? If not,
I'll go back to the hotel and get some.

13:18.628 --> 13:21.887
Yes. I'll get it for you.
They are the hosts. Film them.

13:21.887 --> 13:25.228
Well, I'm the villain.

13:29.488 --> 13:31.808
Three, two, one, begin.

13:31.808 --> 13:35.688
Hello everyone, long time no see.
I am Mo Bai, and here's Mu.

13:35.688 --> 13:36.788
Hello everyone.

13:36.788 --> 13:44.627
It's 6:00 PM in Yangshuo, the sky
is still bright. In 24 hours,

13:44.627 --> 13:50.608
the 10th Anniversary will begin.
We'll have a dubbing show outdoors.

13:50.608 --> 13:52.388
Say something they don't know.

13:52.388 --> 13:53.708
Oh.

13:54.448 --> 13:55.808
Can this part be deleted?

13:55.808 --> 14:00.768
It's live. But no worries,
it's just a behind-the-scenes for fun.

14:00.768 --> 14:02.848
I don't want to be a sketch.

14:02.848 --> 14:05.267
It's okay. Everyone is used to it.

14:06.088 --> 14:07.187
Your turn.

14:09.848 --> 14:12.868
23 hours and 58 minutes left.

14:18.927 --> 14:24.128
Okay, I know Mu is very boring.
You guys just prefer me, right?

14:24.128 --> 14:26.088
So, in the next 24 hours...

14:26.088 --> 14:29.028
It's only 23 hours and 57 minutes left.

14:29.028 --> 14:31.787
Could you please stop the countdown?

14:36.167 --> 14:40.508
Mr. Luan,
come and film our stage, will you?

14:41.208 --> 14:46.068
Our stage is very beautiful. Of course,
we're still under construction.

14:46.068 --> 14:52.008
We also have a small camera
that'll show you the stage construction.

14:52.008 --> 14:55.808
Next, I will take everyone
to tour our surrounding environment.

14:55.808 --> 15:01.108
Let's see if we can meet
some big shots in the show. Follow me.

15:06.488 --> 15:07.628
Follow me.

15:08.647 --> 15:12.667
♪ Listening to the tide by the cliff,
admiring stones in the pavilion ♪

15:12.667 --> 15:16.907
♪ Read all the history books for leisure ♪

15:21.167 --> 15:24.147
- Which one sounds good?
- The second one.

15:25.767 --> 15:27.428
Mr. Wang Ke, Mr. Feishao.

15:27.428 --> 15:28.488
Take a seat.

15:28.488 --> 15:30.308
- Sit.
- Come on.

15:30.308 --> 15:31.948
Sorry, I only ordered two portions.

15:31.948 --> 15:33.348
It's okay, I'm not hungry.

15:33.348 --> 15:35.538
Thank goodness you came along.

15:35.538 --> 15:39.127
Otherwise he'll lose hair
if he can't find the harmony.

15:39.127 --> 15:44.067
We're about to begin.
Let's shake hands before we start.

15:44.647 --> 15:46.548
We've known each other for so long.
Don't be dramatic.

15:46.548 --> 15:51.708
Come on, Doudou. I'm doing this
out of respect. Right, Sheng?

15:51.708 --> 15:54.928
I got this task on short notice.
I'm afraid I might let you down.

15:54.928 --> 15:58.068
It's okay. Sing with confidence.
I've got your back.

15:58.068 --> 15:59.988
Stop it!

15:59.988 --> 16:02.748
Don't you still have rice noodles?
Mine were eaten by Mr. Zhu.

16:02.748 --> 16:08.667
Okay, you eat first. We discussed this
during last night's meeting.

16:08.667 --> 16:13.168
We knew you covered this song before,
so we spoke with Qiang Qingci first.

16:13.168 --> 16:16.520
We were going to tell you directly,
but we were too busy.

16:16.520 --> 16:17.448
Yes, we didn't have time.

16:17.448 --> 16:20.587
How should I harmonize?

16:20.587 --> 16:26.920
I'm so forgetful. Let me explain it.
After section A1, you can enter in A2.

16:26.920 --> 16:33.028
Three pitches higher than me
in the chorus. Then the interval

16:33.028 --> 16:35.408
(A White Horse In The Reeds)
is yours. Don't worry. I've checked.

16:35.408 --> 16:36.487
It's within your vocal range.

16:36.487 --> 16:37.628
You'll be fine.

16:37.628 --> 16:48.128
The resting area. Our main vocals,
Feishao, Wang Ke. Guess who she is.

16:48.128 --> 16:49.088
Hello.

16:49.088 --> 16:52.188
Yes, our long-lost Momo'er.

16:52.188 --> 16:54.207
They keep mentioning this is Doudoubing.

16:54.207 --> 16:58.787
I know, but isn't she going to perform?
So, Momo'er is more suitable.

16:59.448 --> 17:01.888
By the way, let me
introduce one more person to everyone.

17:01.888 --> 17:03.267
Mo Bai.

17:05.047 --> 17:07.948
She's nervous about the first time
being on stage. Leave her be.

17:10.168 --> 17:16.548
And the last one is me. I wanted to
do chorus for Wang Ke, but he rejected.

17:16.548 --> 17:18.608
Bro, aren't you tone-deaf?

17:18.608 --> 17:21.388
They all know it.
There's no need to emphasize again.

17:22.127 --> 17:27.348
All right, I'll take you
to our costume area. Follow me.

17:27.348 --> 17:28.668
Come on, this way.

17:28.668 --> 17:32.448
He's suitable for this.
He's talkative and quick-minded.

17:32.448 --> 17:35.708
I'm done.
When should we start rehearsing?

17:36.527 --> 17:39.068
Give me 10 more minutes.
I will take another bite.

17:39.068 --> 17:41.527
It's okay, take your time.
I will go out and practice first.

17:41.527 --> 17:43.428
- Okay, I'll meet you later.
- Okay.

17:43.428 --> 17:44.988
- Very soon.
- See you in a bit.

17:47.008 --> 17:52.948
She is a bit like Qiang Qingci,
very calm and devoted.

17:53.607 --> 17:57.529
Yes. When I first took the stage,
I was super excited.

17:57.529 --> 18:00.741
But she was into the state pretty quick
and more professional than I thought.

18:07.087 --> 18:08.107
Sheng.

18:09.448 --> 18:10.668
Are you not busy?

18:10.668 --> 18:14.187
I saw you chatting there.
I came over to cheer you on.

18:14.187 --> 18:16.668
I'm so nervous.
I've never been on stage before.

18:16.668 --> 18:19.127
I knew it. Look.

18:19.127 --> 18:22.888
(Guai: Don't be nervous.
Leader: Sheng, come on! We got you!)

18:22.888 --> 18:24.575
They're afraid you can't see it
during the rehearsal.

18:24.575 --> 18:26.446
So they had me show you.

18:27.288 --> 18:29.324
There's no need to be scared.

18:29.348 --> 18:33.408
I'll be with Mao at the control panel.
If you're nervous, just look at me.

18:33.408 --> 18:36.748
Then you'll calm down.
Just like when we're in the school club.

18:36.748 --> 18:37.427
Okay.

18:37.427 --> 18:38.428
Go for it.

18:39.448 --> 18:40.468
What's up?

18:41.488 --> 18:43.568
Well, Mr. Feng.

18:43.568 --> 18:47.547
Silly. When the stage lights are on,
it's hard to see below.

18:50.367 --> 18:53.508
Leave her alone.
She needs to practice with the lyrics.

18:54.168 --> 18:55.608
Sorry.

18:55.608 --> 18:58.368
Let's go. You do your thing. Go.

18:58.368 --> 19:00.028
Go for it.

19:00.028 --> 19:01.348
You too.

19:01.348 --> 19:02.028
I will.

19:02.028 --> 19:03.148
Goodbye.

19:05.408 --> 19:11.087
Left, left. Again. Almost there.

19:11.087 --> 19:13.087
Zhu, it's still not symmetrical.

19:13.087 --> 19:14.547
Wait a moment.

19:22.767 --> 19:25.468
Why are you sitting here alone
and not accompanying Sheng?

19:27.248 --> 19:30.468
She has her own job to do.
My presence there is of no use.

19:31.087 --> 19:34.827
You can be her emotional support
and give her some guidance.

19:36.248 --> 19:37.914
It's her first stage experience.

19:38.347 --> 19:42.354
The anxiety before going onto stage,
trying to cool down, repeated practice,

19:42.354 --> 19:44.648
trying not to make mistakes
and the cooperation with partners.

19:44.648 --> 19:45.794
It'll be a precious memory.

19:45.794 --> 19:49.307
I don't want to interfere
and take away the experience from her.

19:50.208 --> 19:53.827
Are you not her boyfriend?
Why don't you seem nervous?

19:53.827 --> 19:56.488
How do you know I haven't been nervous?

19:56.488 --> 19:58.708
Stop pretending, okay?

19:59.807 --> 20:01.947
Where are you going? Are you worried?

20:01.947 --> 20:03.508
Getting some water.

20:07.448 --> 20:09.388
You...

20:14.488 --> 20:18.664
♪ Riding a horse all day,
reciting hundreds of poems ♪

20:18.664 --> 20:22.368
♪ You were born in an era of peace ♪

20:22.368 --> 20:26.207
♪ Listening to the tide by the cliff,
admiring stones in the pavilion ♪

20:26.207 --> 20:30.547
♪ Read all the history books for leisure ♪

20:45.767 --> 20:47.188
Give her a moment.

20:49.648 --> 20:54.388
Sorry for upstaging you. She becomes
my partner for her first performance.

20:55.448 --> 20:58.267
You are the singer.
It's right for her to be your partner.

20:59.448 --> 21:01.067
This way, she can learn more.

21:01.067 --> 21:02.908
No.

21:03.527 --> 21:05.988
She's really great.

21:20.208 --> 21:21.988
Are you asking me to go rehearse?

21:22.688 --> 21:29.508
She even ignores you when it comes to work.
We'll rehearsal soon, bye.

21:36.928 --> 21:39.547
It's okay. Just be calm.

21:40.928 --> 21:44.867
Anyway, I think
you'll be fine. Because...

21:45.488 --> 21:46.748
You are the best.

21:47.807 --> 21:49.347
I am the best!

21:51.767 --> 21:52.767
Let's go.

22:00.208 --> 22:06.348
The dubbing actors and singers have
returned to Yuerong Manor.

22:06.348 --> 22:11.928
Let's see what they are doing now, okay?
It's very quiet here.

22:11.928 --> 22:16.808
Over there. Isn't there
someone from Perfect Voice?

22:16.808 --> 22:19.528
After this matter has settled,
continue to live as siblings.

22:19.528 --> 22:23.027
If I can do treason,
why can't I marry Zhaozhao?

22:24.807 --> 22:27.752
(Live stream interaction)
I can hardly see from the comments.

22:27.752 --> 22:35.248
"Is Qiang Qingci there?"
Keep guessing. Follow me.

22:35.248 --> 22:41.988
I know you want a closer look,
but I won't give you the chance.

22:44.408 --> 22:49.067
(6 hours before the performance)
Good. Nice! Okay, take a break.

22:49.648 --> 22:51.608
Mao, it's ready.

22:51.608 --> 22:52.328
Okay.

22:52.328 --> 22:56.572
(Ten years of dreams and love)
The supper is over there.

22:56.744 --> 23:01.628
After that, the final rehearsal.

23:01.628 --> 23:06.827
I know it's hot. Bear with it, okay?
Hurry up and eat, come on.

23:07.928 --> 23:09.068
You got yours, Zheng?

23:09.068 --> 23:10.288
Zhou Zheng, yours?

23:10.288 --> 23:11.168
Yes.

23:11.168 --> 23:11.807
Okay.

23:11.807 --> 23:13.148
Share with everyone.

23:16.488 --> 23:17.587
Do you want it?

23:21.448 --> 23:23.607
Leave some for him.
Don't eat them all by yourself.

23:23.607 --> 23:24.828
Is this a steamed bun?

23:24.828 --> 23:26.587
It has fillings.

23:28.527 --> 23:31.547
The osmanthus cakes Mr. Qiang ordered
taste pretty good.

23:32.488 --> 23:34.388
Osmanthus cake. Just arrived.

23:34.388 --> 23:35.827
Thank you.

23:42.928 --> 23:45.948
I have fallen in love with this place.
Everything here tastes delicious.

23:49.728 --> 23:50.908
Are you nervous?

23:53.488 --> 23:58.587
I don't feel it now, but I will
when they start the one-hour countdown.

23:59.767 --> 24:04.508
It's a good thing.
It means you respect the stage.

24:05.688 --> 24:07.228
You talk like an instructor.

24:07.767 --> 24:09.228
Our chill pill.

24:09.807 --> 24:11.408
Why chill pill?

24:11.408 --> 24:14.183
No matter what we perform,
stage performances or dubbing dramas,

24:14.183 --> 24:15.510
he's the chill pill

24:15.510 --> 24:19.090
because he'll keep everything in check
behind the stage.

24:23.408 --> 24:24.468
What?

24:25.168 --> 24:27.948
Realizing your choice is not bad?

24:28.767 --> 24:30.508
I've always had good taste.

24:31.688 --> 24:33.468
When to do the makeup and get changed?

24:34.448 --> 24:35.428
After a while, maybe.

24:35.428 --> 24:37.428
Then I will go and take a look.

24:41.127 --> 24:45.528
Please don't.
If you go, I will get nervous.

24:45.528 --> 24:47.988
I haven't seen it. I'd like to see you.

24:47.988 --> 24:50.347
Watch me on the stage, alright?

24:51.607 --> 24:52.607
Okay.

25:22.607 --> 25:25.488
Mao, how is it?
Is there any problem here?

25:25.488 --> 25:28.167
No problem on my side.
How about things over there?

25:28.167 --> 25:31.808
Right. How are the actors now?

25:31.808 --> 25:34.567
All actors and singers are in place
and ready to go.

25:34.567 --> 25:39.268
Everyone, we are now fully dressed
because there are only ten minutes left.

25:39.268 --> 25:43.868
It's about to start. Let's take five.
We will formally meet afterwards.

25:43.868 --> 25:44.888
Okay.

25:44.888 --> 25:46.648
Here, we'll move to the waiting area.

25:46.648 --> 25:47.827
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

25:59.127 --> 26:01.827
- Anyone else in the entrance passage?
- Okay.

26:05.840 --> 26:09.032
(Return With You)

26:09.056 --> 26:14.303
♪ Touching the crack with my fingertips ♪

26:14.303 --> 26:19.413
♪ I dare not look at the haggard faces
and gray hair in the mirror ♪

26:19.413 --> 26:25.630
♪ After many years,
the longing remains as sharp ♪

26:26.968 --> 26:30.347
Qiang Qingci.

26:31.807 --> 26:35.988
It's Shengshengman. Qiang Qingci
and her actually sang a duet.

26:37.567 --> 26:40.587
Qiang Qingci.

26:41.406 --> 26:44.576
♪ The bronze mirror shatters at farewell ♪

26:44.576 --> 26:46.750
♪ It's hard to convey the lovesickness ♪

26:46.750 --> 26:51.378
♪ Over millions of miles ♪

26:51.956 --> 26:55.518
♪ I laugh at the fame
and wealth of my life ♪

26:55.518 --> 26:57.497
♪ I picture it as a flower in the mirror ♪

26:57.497 --> 27:02.622
♪ It's hard to rival
a cup of tea in your hand ♪

27:02.622 --> 27:04.254
♪ We drink from the same cup ♪

27:04.254 --> 27:06.206
♪ And we share joy and sorrow ♪

27:06.206 --> 27:09.059
♪ We drink down the past memories ♪

27:09.059 --> 27:13.726
♪ Being together from morning till night ♪

27:13.726 --> 27:17.086
♪ Or alone in the corner of the world ♪

27:17.086 --> 27:19.093
♪ Frost whitens the hair
in front of the forehead ♪

27:19.093 --> 27:24.754
♪ Looking at the world, where is my home ♪

27:26.127 --> 27:27.307
I can't believe it.

27:27.968 --> 27:29.307
Me, too.

27:33.968 --> 27:35.768
You're not going onstage. Why dress up?

27:35.768 --> 27:38.307
The 10th Anniversary is different.

27:48.728 --> 27:52.128
30 seconds countdown.
Everyone, be prepared.

27:52.128 --> 27:55.267
Come on, everyone, gather around.
It's countdown time.

27:56.008 --> 27:57.008
Here.

27:58.168 --> 27:59.768
The 10th Anniversary of Perfect Voice.

27:59.768 --> 28:00.948
Go!

28:00.948 --> 28:01.928
I'm going onstage.

28:01.928 --> 28:03.748
- Go!
- Go!

28:05.823 --> 28:08.028
(Ten years of dreams and love)

28:14.168 --> 28:17.587
- Juemei!
- Juemei!

28:18.527 --> 28:21.023
Ten years of dreams and love.

28:21.023 --> 28:26.748
Hi guys! Good evening!
Welcome to Yangshuo, Guilin,

28:26.748 --> 28:35.228
to celebrate our 10th Anniversary.
We welcome online viewers, too.

28:35.228 --> 28:42.388
We'd like to thank Yuanbao Investment
and Fufu App for promotion.

28:42.388 --> 28:46.388
I am your host Juemei Shayi.

28:50.087 --> 28:54.048
Juemei!

28:54.048 --> 28:59.867
That's our theme song, Return With You,
by Qiang Qingci and Shengshengman.

28:59.867 --> 29:04.327
That's our surprise for you.
Do you all like it?

29:04.327 --> 29:06.347
Yes!

29:06.347 --> 29:08.347
But this is the only song
featuring them.

29:10.448 --> 29:18.488
Next, let's enjoy some traditional songs
and the touching dubbing show.

29:20.488 --> 29:24.430
Everyone likes Jiangnan
and travelers should settle down here.

29:24.430 --> 29:28.307
Please enjoy, Memories of Jiangnan.

29:32.287 --> 29:34.228
Get ready. Stand by.

29:51.928 --> 29:54.408
It's on! Finally.

29:54.408 --> 29:57.168
My god, this stage is just awesome.

29:57.168 --> 29:59.948
(Shen Zhaozhao doesn't know
how many days the rain's been falling.)

29:59.948 --> 30:03.388
Don't be nervous.

30:04.327 --> 30:07.708
Stabilize it a bit in the high pitch.
Steady, yes.

30:08.847 --> 30:10.388
Perfect Voice is the best.

30:10.388 --> 30:12.047
More than 17 million viewers
in less than an hour.

30:12.047 --> 30:12.688
Really?

30:12.688 --> 30:16.488
The last scene may reach 20 million.
Come on.

30:16.488 --> 30:20.288
Stop talking, don't make Sheng nervous.
I'm getting a bit nervous here.

30:20.288 --> 30:22.708
It'll reach 50 million
as soon as she's on stage.

30:53.688 --> 30:54.748
Zhaozhao.

30:58.087 --> 30:59.188
Brother.

31:12.847 --> 31:14.948
I shouldn't have kept you in Chaisang.

31:21.607 --> 31:22.787
Brother.

31:24.047 --> 31:27.587
Just tell me.

31:33.648 --> 31:34.827
Marry...

31:39.047 --> 31:40.148
Me.

31:44.648 --> 31:46.787
Go find the red cloth.

31:49.208 --> 31:52.588
General, the palace is in chaos.
There's nowhere to find the red cloth.

31:52.588 --> 31:56.148
Go find it. Go!

31:56.148 --> 32:00.708
Here, tonight,

32:02.408 --> 32:03.988
I'll marry Zhaozhao.

32:06.488 --> 32:10.768
General, she is your sister in name.
Everyone knows.

32:10.768 --> 32:12.128
So what?

32:12.128 --> 32:21.188
No! Half of those generals are disloyal.
They wanted to rebel. If you do it,

32:21.188 --> 32:23.004
it will just give them an excuse.

32:23.752 --> 32:30.388
The emperor is dead now.
It's your opportunity to seize power!

32:33.648 --> 32:34.988
Go.

32:36.847 --> 32:38.787
Find the red cloth.

32:44.168 --> 32:48.787
I'll leave the realm
to the crown prince.

32:51.648 --> 32:56.827
And I will marry Zhaozhao.

32:57.408 --> 33:03.208
If you want to be with her,
wait until this matter is settled.

33:03.208 --> 33:07.867
If I can do treason,
why can't I marry Zhaozhao?

33:16.008 --> 33:21.428
Why must they kill Shen Zhaozhao?

33:22.168 --> 33:28.148
I have millions of soldiers,
but I still can't protect Zhaozhao.

33:29.047 --> 33:31.148
In order to protect me,

33:31.728 --> 33:34.948
she was hidden in our house for years.

33:35.607 --> 33:40.228
Afterwards,
she followed me through battles.

33:41.567 --> 33:42.827
And now,

33:44.527 --> 33:47.948
she ended her life to protect me.

33:48.807 --> 33:54.228
Can't I at least marry her today?

34:08.368 --> 34:14.508
Shen Ce, courtesy name Muye,
born into a noble family and handsome.

34:14.760 --> 34:19.187
Lived humbly with his sister
when young.

34:19.928 --> 34:21.839
He was knighted
because of his skills in battle.

34:21.839 --> 34:24.111
He fueled war with warfare.

34:24.704 --> 34:28.850
He was violent and suspicious.
A cunning but resourceful man.

34:28.936 --> 34:32.008
The royals feared his ruthlessness
and imprisoned his sister.

34:32.008 --> 34:34.556
They wanted him to be controlled.

34:35.660 --> 34:41.027
His troop approached the capital,
but his sister took her own life.

34:43.127 --> 34:44.828
Ce was infuriated.

34:45.607 --> 34:48.508
He set fire to the palace
and assassinated the emperor.

34:50.448 --> 34:52.468
The world was shocked.

34:53.527 --> 34:56.828
Rumors has it
that on the day the palace fell,

34:57.687 --> 35:00.067
Shen Ce, on his horse,

35:00.928 --> 35:03.707
left the palace,
carrying a woman in red.

35:04.247 --> 35:08.147
And no traces of them were found since.

35:08.727 --> 35:11.868
The realm became leaderless.

35:12.527 --> 35:14.067
The South

35:16.647 --> 35:18.027
was in a great chaos.

35:29.527 --> 35:32.747
Mao, it's your turn. Go on.

35:38.349 --> 35:45.980
(A White Horse In The Reeds)

35:47.888 --> 35:49.428
Wang Ke.

35:51.167 --> 35:53.687
♪ The Yellow River flows from the Sky ♪

35:53.687 --> 35:56.468
♪ Rushes into famous poems ♪

35:58.687 --> 36:01.088
♪ Clouds atop the ridge
turn into snow in Luoyang ♪

36:01.088 --> 36:04.067
♪ Covering all among the mountains ♪

36:06.488 --> 36:10.668
♪ The light of Xijing is like the sea ♪

36:10.668 --> 36:14.368
♪ The winds blow through the tower ♪

36:14.368 --> 36:19.627
♪ Looking up,
the scene turns into desolate smoke ♪

36:21.448 --> 36:24.087
♪ I once traveled
along the Chang'an Road ♪

36:24.087 --> 36:26.468
♪ Entering the wilderness ♪

36:26.468 --> 36:28.308
Sheng.

36:29.127 --> 36:31.808
♪ The messenger
inadvertently carries souls beneath ♪

36:31.808 --> 36:34.488
♪ The ruined stele
is buried into the deep snow ♪

36:34.488 --> 36:36.348
Sheng.

36:37.008 --> 36:38.008
Why does Sheng take the stage?

36:38.008 --> 36:40.968
♪ The dream is piercingly cold ♪

36:40.968 --> 36:43.368
Shengshengman, come on!

36:43.368 --> 36:45.068
- Come on!
- Come on!

36:45.068 --> 36:50.687
♪ An elegant figure ascends the palace ♪

36:50.687 --> 36:54.607
♪ Standing proud before the emperor ♪

36:54.607 --> 36:57.607
♪ The silver bowl is filled with snow.
The bright moon hides the heron ♪

36:57.607 --> 37:02.087
♪ A white horse in the reeds ♪

37:02.087 --> 37:03.848
♪ Sounds of the flute ♪

37:03.848 --> 37:08.928
♪ Travelers go through the world,
with a lantern in their hands ♪

37:08.928 --> 37:13.368
♪ Climbing up to see the landscape ♪

37:13.368 --> 37:17.448
♪ Watching the rosy clouds
at the burial ground ♪

37:17.448 --> 37:18.488
♪ It's hard to cross the border ♪

37:18.488 --> 37:24.348
♪ Who in Chang'an
still talks about heroes ♪

37:56.928 --> 37:59.288
♪ I once traveled
along the Chang'an Road ♪

37:59.288 --> 38:02.107
♪ Entering the wilderness ♪

38:04.607 --> 38:06.888
♪ The messenger
inadvertently carries souls beneath ♪

38:06.888 --> 38:10.027
♪ The ruined stele
is buried into the deep snow ♪

38:12.087 --> 38:16.768
♪ In my song,
the dream is piercingly cold ♪

38:16.768 --> 38:20.128
♪ The lone moon is hanging high ♪

38:20.128 --> 38:26.247
♪ An elegant figure ascends the palace ♪

38:26.247 --> 38:29.328
♪ Standing proud before the emperor ♪

38:29.328 --> 38:32.687
♪ The silver bowl is filled with snow.
The bright moon hides the heron ♪

38:32.687 --> 38:37.248
♪ A white horse in the reeds ♪

38:37.248 --> 38:40.607
♪ The everlasting charms
remind me of him ♪

38:40.607 --> 38:42.027
(Hello, Sheng.)

38:43.087 --> 38:44.168
I am Qiang Qingci.

38:44.168 --> 38:46.167
♪ In the quiet night,
I was drunk on the stage ♪

38:46.167 --> 38:47.168
Hello.

38:47.168 --> 38:48.647
♪ Lying in prime of life ♪

38:48.647 --> 38:51.207
♪ Let the stars shine on the roof,
like a swift sandstorm ♪

38:51.207 --> 38:52.547
(Thank you for accompanying me.)

38:52.547 --> 38:53.247
♪ Beneath the desk ♪

38:53.247 --> 38:53.888
(I like you a lot.)

38:53.888 --> 38:55.647
♪ He represents
the flourishing Tang Dynasty ♪

38:55.647 --> 38:57.227
Be my girlfriend.

38:59.687 --> 39:03.448
♪ Riding a horse all day,
reciting hundreds of poems ♪

39:03.448 --> 39:07.248
♪ You were born in an era of peace ♪

39:07.248 --> 39:11.108
♪ Listening to the tide by the cliff,
admiring stones in the pavilion ♪

39:11.108 --> 39:15.488
♪ Read all the history books for leisure ♪

39:15.488 --> 39:19.247
♪ The ashes in the cup.
The waning moon overhead ♪

39:19.247 --> 39:22.968
♪ People stand on withered grass.
Tombstones stand on the mound ♪

39:22.968 --> 39:30.607
♪ Feeling the vastness of all ages,
the void is draped with white silk ♪

39:30.607 --> 39:33.607
♪ The silver bowl is filled with snow.
The bright moon hides the heron ♪

39:33.607 --> 39:38.087
♪ A white horse in the reeds ♪

39:38.087 --> 39:45.247
♪ The everlasting charms
remind me of him ♪

39:45.247 --> 39:48.308
♪ In the quiet night,
I was drunk on the stage ♪

39:48.308 --> 39:49.567
♪ Lying in prime of life ♪

39:49.567 --> 39:53.488
♪ Let the stars shine on the roof,
like a swift sandstorm ♪

39:53.488 --> 40:01.147
♪ Beneath the desk, he represents
the flourishing Tang Dynasty ♪

40:03.328 --> 40:05.067
Wang Ke, I love you.

40:23.527 --> 40:25.268
Bravo!

40:27.008 --> 40:29.348
Perfect Voice!

40:31.288 --> 40:33.627
Perfect Voice!

40:35.727 --> 40:42.567
Guys, the 10th Anniversary
of Perfect Voice comes to an end.

40:42.567 --> 40:47.027
Let's look forward
to the next reunion! Bye!

40:51.488 --> 40:53.587
Perfect Voice!

40:54.247 --> 40:56.348
Perfect Voice!

41:21.888 --> 41:26.568
My hands and feet were ice cold.
I was afraid I'd mess up.

41:26.568 --> 41:30.107
You're incredibly beautiful,
as if you stepped out of a painting.

41:31.527 --> 41:34.288
Wait, I'd like to know if I sang well.

41:34.288 --> 41:37.428
- Bravo, I was moved to tears, Sheng.
- Really?

41:37.428 --> 41:38.908
You see, my face is still red.

41:38.908 --> 41:41.067
It's really hot.

41:42.408 --> 41:47.687
Since you're performing together
for the first time, can you encore?

41:47.687 --> 41:48.368
Yes.

41:48.368 --> 41:49.047
What is it?

41:49.047 --> 41:49.908
There's more?

41:49.908 --> 41:51.468
- There's more!
- Encore!

41:51.468 --> 41:52.147
There's more!

41:52.147 --> 42:00.147
- Encore!
- Encore!

42:03.902 --> 42:07.050
♪ Meteor flies to the edge of the sky ♪

42:07.050 --> 42:09.725
♪ Crossing the horizon ♪

42:10.138 --> 42:12.616
♪ The wind listens to all the wishes ♪

42:12.616 --> 42:15.122
♪ Fluttering memories ♪

42:15.751 --> 42:18.886
♪ Sunshine through the dancing leaves ♪

42:18.910 --> 42:21.926
♪ Falls on the boy's shoulder ♪

42:21.950 --> 42:24.520
♪ The journey of youth has no end ♪

42:24.520 --> 42:27.058
♪ Year by year ♪

42:27.528 --> 42:30.641
♪ Rain will pass by your window ♪

42:30.641 --> 42:32.732
♪ Then run towards the sunny day ♪

42:33.614 --> 42:36.232
♪ Dreams await at the start
of our encounter ♪

42:36.232 --> 42:38.588
♪ Touching the fingertips ♪

42:39.434 --> 42:42.167
♪ Longing for the world in your eyes ♪

42:42.167 --> 42:45.577
♪ The unspoken understanding
reflects in our gaze ♪

42:45.577 --> 42:50.140
♪ You smile,
and get a little closer to me ♪

42:51.390 --> 42:53.256
♪ I want to go with you ♪

42:53.256 --> 42:56.381
♪ To a farther future ♪

42:56.381 --> 42:58.632
♪ Dreams can reach the other shore ♪

42:58.632 --> 43:02.555
♪ I really like you a lot ♪

43:02.555 --> 43:05.499
♪ The first time I am brave ♪

43:05.499 --> 43:09.083
♪ Looking up,
chasing the momentary fireworks ♪

